Massimo '''"Atomic"''' Franceschi {{born}} is an [[:category:United States|American]] ''Rocket League'' player. [[Atomic]] was involved in a [[RLRS]] ban in 2017, by illegally subbing in the play-ins when he was an underage and unregistered player. His team at the time, [[Naventic]], released him and his teammates, and the RLCS/RLRS admins banned him from [[Rocket_League_Championship_Series/Season_4/North_America/Rocket_League_Rival_Series|RLCS S4 - RLRS]] and other Psyonix sponsored seasons and tournaments until June 30th, 2019.
